#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
#include<algorithm>

int main(){
	
	string a[20001];
	int count[20001],ans[20001],chk,m;
	int i,n;
	while(1){
		
		cin >> n >> m;
		
		if(n==0 && m==0)
		break;
		
		else{
			
			chk=0;
			for(i=0;i<n;++i)
	        cin >>a[i];
	
	        for(i=0;i<n;++i){
	        
	            count[i]=1;
 	            ans[i]=0;
			}
			sort(a,a+n);
	        
	        
			for(i=0;i<n;++i){
				int j=i;
				while(a[i]==a[i+1]){
					//cout << "1\n";
					++count[j];
					
					++i;
				}
				if(count[j]==1)
				++chk;
				
				
			}
			
			
			sort(count,count+n);
			
			//for(i=0;i<n;++i)
			//cout << count[i]<<" ";
			
			for(i=0;i<n;++i){
				
				if(count[i]>1)
				ans[count[i]]=1;
			}
			
			for(i=0;i<n;++i){
				
				if(count[i]>1){
					
					while(i<n){
						
						int j=i;
						while(count[i]==count[i+1]){
						
						    ++ans[count[j]];
						    ++i;
 						}
						++i;
					}
					
					break;
					
				}
			
			
			}
			
			cout << chk <<"\n";
			for(i=2;i<=n;++i)
			cout <<ans[i]<<"\n";
			
		}
		
		
		
		
	}
	
	return 0;
}
